        <div class="description">
            The Origin Portal was built to allow employers to seek out origin grads who meet their criteria. Once employers
            search for students who meet the criteria, they can then look at those students profiles and contact them directly.
            This web app was built using react-redux, bootstrap, CSS, Nodejs and runs of an express server. Legacy code already 
            existed for this application, so it was my first experince delving into a code base that had already been set. I 
            worked in a team of 6 utilizing the Git workflow to keep everything in order. We quickly realized the value of using
            Git and the need to adhear to certian workflow guide-lines to ensure quality code. This project was both fun and challengeing
            to work with. I look forward to other challengeing projects!
